      • Physicaloid

        public Physicaloid(android.content.Context context,
                   boolean u,
                   java.lang.String BlueName,
                   java.lang.String Netdest,
                   int Dport,
                   int Cport)
        Parameters:
        context -
        u - true = use USB
        BlueName - Name of bluetooth, null for automatic default
        Netdest - e.g. "192.168.4.1" or a host name, null defaults to "192.168.4.1"
        Dport - port number for data, Zero = 9001
        Cport - port number for controls, Zero = Dport + 1
